{"change_summary":"No additional code edits were required in this plan-and-implement turn. The existing milestone_record implementation already tracks explicit milestone/task/run linkage, supports updating and querying bead attempts through the filesystem adapter, preserves retry audit history, and remains valid after fresh workspace revalidation.","outstanding_risks":["Milestone mutations still span separate lineage, snapshot, and journal files without a cross-file transaction, so a crash between file writes can still leave snapshot or journal state temporarily behind `task-runs.ndjson` until the same operation is replayed or state is reconciled from lineage.","Manually corrupted lineage that already contains multiple simultaneous open attempts for the same bead still rejects new starts or runless completions as ambiguous until the bad state is repaired or richer caller metadata is supplied."],"steps":[{"description":"Reviewed the current workspace and bead state, confirming `ralph-burning-9ni.2.4` is already closed and there was no new milestone_record implementation gap to patch.","order":0,"status":"completed"},{"description":"Revalidated the existing milestone_record implementation in the current workspace with formatting, targeted unit tests, and clippy.","order":1,"status":"completed"},{"description":"Prepared this execution payload to carry forward the approved implementation details and current residual risks without making further code changes.","order":2,"status":"completed"}],"validation_evidence":["`git status --short` showed no tracked source-file modifications; only an untracked `.ralph-burning/` directory was present.","`br show ralph-burning-9ni.2.4` confirmed the bead is closed as `Completed`.","`cargo fmt --all --check` completed successfully.","`cargo test --lib contexts::milestone_record` passed with 105 tests.","`cargo clippy -- -D warnings` completed successfully."]}